In the Matter of Y.Q.M.
appealed by Shanita Fryar, Respondent. No. 260P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 17, 2006. Winifred H. Dillon, Raleigh, for Shanita Fryar. Corinne Railey, for Sampson County DSS. S. Nicole Taylor, Raleigh, for Guardian ad Litem.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed on the 9th day of May 2006 by Respondent (Shanita Fryar) in this matter for discretionary review of the decision of the North Carolina Court of Appeals pursuant to G.S. 7A-31, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 17th day of August 2006."
